UV and LDR Sensor
This project aims to read data from a UV sensor and an LDR sensor and display the results on an LCD screen. The UV sensor will display the UV index and the LDR sensor will display the light intensity.

Components
Arduino Uno
LiquidCrystal Library
UV sensor

Installation
Connect the UV sensor to analog pin A5 on the Arduino board

Connect the LCD screen to the following pins on the Arduino board:
RS: 8
E: 9
D4: 4
D5: 5
D6: 6
D7: 7
Upload the code to the Arduino board
Usage
Connect the Arduino board to power
Press the UV button to display the UV index
Contributing
Contributions are welcome. Please make sure to update the tests as appropriate.

